{"tid":1556922,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"登左報要求港鐵交代831真相，而家號召大家再去信港鐵","createTime":"2019-09-10T02:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T04:06:05.000Z","uid":264565,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0426693c66bfbf53b9ae1cfce701c9e60a18c7d8","tid":1556922,"uid":264565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:21:54.000Z","msg":"各位手足，感激大家參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，雞蛋撞石牆，希望我哋可以快啲知道真相！報紙已出了，鼓勵各手足藉此去信港鐵要求交代！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家可以用以下template：<br />\n<br />\n港鐵網站提供網上意見：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/feedback.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcustomer%2Fmain%2Ffeedback.php&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=737745d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/feedback.php</a><br />\n<br />\n港鐵董事會主席歐陽伯權先生（investor@mtr.com.hk）<br />\n<br />\n本人作為香港市民，一直以港鐵作為日常交通工具，亦常在地下旗下的商户購物，體驗到港鐵正如口號提及「心繫生活每一程」。<br />\n<br />\n本人明白到港鐵為上市公司，以賺取利潤為前提是無可厚非；但本人仍選擇認為港鐵會重視市民，保障乘搭港鐵的市民的安全。誠如港鐵先前就721元朗站發生的事故，於6日後向公眾公開相關資料。這個做法能有效釋除市民疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n惟在831太子站事故當日及隔天無故封站多個小時，港鐵事發至今沒有公開相關資料，令社會各方有不同揣測；而此舉亦著實影響港鐵的專業形象。<br />\n<br />\n本人與一眾關心是次事件的市民，於今日（2019年9月10日）在明報的A9及蘋果日報的A5，刊登名為「還原真相，釋疑解惑」一群香港市民致港鐵的公開信（隨函附上公開信內容），懇請港鐵董事會成員、管理層和職員，能夠盡快公開有關831事故當日及隔日的完整閉路電視錄影及港鐵職員隨身錄影裝置片段。<br />\n<br />\n香港市民 xxx<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明報同蘋果<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kt1sGfJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKt1sGfJ.png&h=5fe11283&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HJPJY2r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHJPJY2r.png&h=7e3e6ad0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立場報導<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%80%E7%BE%A4%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%A8%E5%A0%B1%E7%AB%A0%E7%99%BB%E5%85%A8%E7%89%88%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E4%BF%A1-%E4%BF%83%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B-831-%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99-cctv-%E5%8F%8A%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E9%9A%A8%E8%BA%AB%E9%8C%84%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5/#.XXbpX71x_4E.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25AB%25A0%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2589%2588%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E4%25BF%25A1-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B-831-%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%2599-cctv-%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%259A%25A8%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E9%258C%2584%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%2F%23.XXbpX71x_4E.facebook&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=bac3c4f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25AB%25A0%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2589%2588%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E4%25BF%25A1-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B-831-%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%2599-cctv-%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%259A%25A8%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E9%258C%2584%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%2F%23.XXbpX71x_4E.facebook&h=2f819846\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%80%E7%BE%A4%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%A8%E5%A0%B1%E7%AB%A0%E7%99%BB%E5%85%A8%E7%89%88%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E4%BF%A1-%E4%BF%83%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B-831-%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99-cctv-%E5%8F%8A%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E9%9A%A8%E8%BA%AB%E9%8C%84%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5/#.XXbpX71x_4E.facebook</a>"},{"pid":"4f807b316e99251a277a5d55e90465f4ddb6475c","tid":1556922,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:29:42.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n<br />\n第四期Link :